# GitHub Final Project

This is the final project repository for demonstrating Git and GitHub workflows.  
It includes essential community files such as README, LICENSE, CONTRIBUTING, and CODE OF CONDUCT.

## Features
- Demonstrates Git CLI operations (branching, merging, reverting, etc.)
- Includes a sample shell script (simple-interest.sh)
- Follows best practices for open-source projects

